# VIP Starter 基础规则

优先读取的 canonical docs：

- `product-design-kit/guide/agent-usage.md`
- `product-design-kit/guide/large-projects.md`
- `product-design-kit/design/design-init.md`
- `product-design-kit/design/product-design.md`
- `project/ui-brand.md`
- `project/overview.md`

工作边界：

- 规范只从 `product-design-kit/` 读取
- 项目状态与领域文档只写到 `project/`
- 代码只写到 `src/`
- 默认围绕单个领域推进
- 不要重新引入并行的旧流程目录

实现时优先参考：

- `product-design-kit/guide/repo-structure.md`
- 列表页优先参考 `product-design-kit/coding/react-list-page.md`
- 标签页或子页容器优先参考 `product-design-kit/coding/react-tabs-page.md`
- 文档与代码一致性优先参考 `product-design-kit/coding/consistency.md`
